data.description: All celltypes umap coordinates were calculated for a sobset of 800k cells.
data.annotation_details: To unify cell type labels across the studies, we re-annotated all cells into 58 immune cell types, grouped into 10 major compartments: B cells, CD4 T cells, TRAV1-2⁻ CD8 T cells, mucosal associated invariant T (MAIT) cells, γδ T cells, double-negative (DN) T cells, innate lymphoid cells (ILCs), NK cells, myeloid cells, and progenitors
